{"id": "18124", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=18124", "title": "Arnie's House", "text": "The house by the &lt;a href=\"Archer%27s%20Guild%20%28building%29\"&gt;Archer's Guild&lt;/a&gt; is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20locations\"&gt;location&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Ferol\"&gt;Ferol&lt;/a&gt;. It can be found east of the &lt;a href=\"Archer%27s%20Guild%20%28building%29\"&gt;Archer's Guild&lt;/a&gt;. It was the home of &lt;a href=\"Arnie\"&gt;Arnie&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Penny\"&gt;Penny&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Timmy\"&gt;Timmy&lt;/a&gt; until &lt;a href=\"Raven\"&gt;Raven&lt;/a&gt; and his thugs appeared, taking Arnie and Penny as hostages.\nLayout.\nApart from hostage situation, there is not much to do in the house. There are only three rooms: a living room, a bedroom and a kitchen.\nThere are visible signs of fighting in the living room: a broken table and a barrel, as well as some items on the floor.\nThere is also a &lt;a href=\"Cask%20of%20Ale\"&gt;Cask of Ale&lt;/a&gt; and an &lt;a href=\"Empty%20Mug\"&gt;Empty Mug&lt;/a&gt; in the living room, right next to the kitchen door.\nInterior doors to the kitchen and the bedroom are locked, as well as the exterior northern doors. The kitchen door key is under the tree, right outside the kitchen. Inside the kitchen is a key to the bedroom exterior door. A composite key which opens the kitchen door form inside can be found on the bedroom table.\nRaven drops the key for the cupboard, with holds the sapphire key.\nWith the sapphire key, &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; can open the locked chest in the bedroom."}
