{"id": "14722", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14722", "title": "Augmentor", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20miscellaneous%20items\"&gt;miscellaneous item&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nA plant native to &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt;, augmentor is a powerful &lt;a href=\"alchemy\"&gt;alchemy&lt;/a&gt; ingredient, allowing alchemists to create the largest of &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20Consumables\"&gt;Potions&lt;/a&gt; when used with other mixtures."}
{"id": "19075", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19075", "title": "Augmentor (Original Sin 2)", "text": "The is a type of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20consumables%23Herbs\"&gt;herb&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nAugmentor is a herb that can be found freely growing in both the wilderness of Rivellon or in the gardens of its denizens. It is a herb prized for its capability to improve potions or, on its own, to create potions increasing &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; attribute. Unlike most herbs Augmentor comes in three varieties which differ in shape and quality, with higher quality varieties having stronger effects. Like most other consumable items, if character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; the strength increasing effects of augmentor will be doubled.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of herbs and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs.\nUsage.\nFollowing table shows all items for which this item is used for. Note that for more powerful potions a better quality Augmentor is required. If the item utilises base Augmentor it is possible to use higher quality Augmentor as substitute. In short you cannot use \"Augmentor\" in recipe requiring \"Ultimate Augmentor Herb\" or \"High Quality Augmentor\"."}
{"id": "17627", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17627", "title": "Augmentor Seedling", "text": "Augmentor seedling is a type of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20miscellaneous%20items\"&gt;miscellaneous item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nA bucket with growing &lt;a href=\"Augmentor%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Augmentor&lt;/a&gt; seedling. Place it unto ground for it to begin growing. After 2 turns the seedling will grow into harvestable herb which produces random amount of Augmentor, ranging from 1 to 3 herbs.\nAfter harvesting the herb the &lt;a href=\"Bucket\"&gt;Bucket&lt;/a&gt; used will become &lt;a href=\"Clay-filled%20bucket\"&gt;Clay-filled bucket&lt;/a&gt;."}
