{"id": "8973", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8973", "title": "Baldini", "text": "Baldini is the &lt;a href=\"ghost\"&gt;ghost&lt;/a&gt; of man found at the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Nimir\"&gt;Temple of Nimir&lt;/a&gt; under &lt;a href=\"Lanilor%20Lane\"&gt;Lanilor Lane&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; in 1300 AD.\nBackground.\nThe uncle of the &lt;a href=\"alchemist\"&gt;alchemist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"illusionist\"&gt;illusionist&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Chanelle\"&gt;Chanelle&lt;/a&gt;, Baldini was a perfumer to kings and queens before his untimely demise. Having worked with all the aromas in the know the known world, he set out to find the &lt;a href=\"flower%20that%20doesn%27t%20exist\"&gt;flower that doesn't exist&lt;/a&gt;. His nose led him to the temple in search of the rarest scent in &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt;, where he ascended the platforms and fell to his death after being overwhelmed by the smell of the flower he found there."}
{"id": "8970", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8970", "title": "Baldini's Bouquet", "text": ""}
{"id": "8971", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8971", "title": "Baldini's Bouquet (item)", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divinity%20II%20quest%20items%23Flames%20of%20Vengeance\"&gt;quest item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\"\nCharacteristics.\nBaldini's Bouquet is a unique perfume crafted from the rarest flower in &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"ghost\"&gt;ghost&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Baldini\"&gt;Baldini&lt;/a&gt; asks the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; to harvest &lt;a href=\"the%20Flower%20that%20doesn%27t%20Exist\"&gt;the Flower that doesn't Exist&lt;/a&gt; from a high ledge in the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Nimir\"&gt;Temple of Nimir&lt;/a&gt; during the quest &lt;a href=\"Baldini%27s%20Bouquet%20%28quest%29\"&gt;Baldini's Bouquet&lt;/a&gt;.\nLocations.\nOnce acquired, the flower is taken to his niece &lt;a href=\"Chanelle\"&gt;Chanelle&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Chez%20Chanelle\"&gt;Chez Chanelle&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Lanilor%20Lane\"&gt;Lanilor Lane&lt;/a&gt;. She crafts this perfume using the flower."}
{"id": "3827", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3827", "title": "Baldini's Bouquet (quest)", "text": "Baldini's Bouquet is a &lt;a href=\"Flames%20of%20Vengeance%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; received from &lt;a href=\"Baldini\"&gt;Baldini&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"ghost\"&gt;ghost&lt;/a&gt; located in the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Nimir\"&gt;Temple of Nimir&lt;/a&gt; under &lt;a href=\"Lanilor%20Lane\"&gt;Lanilor Lane&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt;.\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nBefore you can accept this quest you need to complete &lt;a href=\"Old%20Dog%20or%20New%20Tricks%3F\"&gt;Old Dog or New Tricks?&lt;/a&gt; side quest in order to unlock the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Nimir\"&gt;Temple of Nimir&lt;/a&gt;.\nInside the temple head straight and then turn right, go down the cave into old temple ruins where you will find the spirit of the deceased perfumer &lt;a href=\"Baldini\"&gt;Baldini&lt;/a&gt;. He will ask you to retrieve the flower which is located above.\nHead over to the ladder in the northwest corner and climb up. Continue up the second ladder and pull the lever, which lowers a nearby ladder. Without descending, turn around and jump across to the platform in the southwest corner. Flip the pull the lever here to lower another ladder.\nWalk off the edge of the platform and fall to the ground. Climb up the ladders you've just lowered, jump across (south) to the nearby platform, then turn left (east) and jump to the next platform. Pull the lever to activate the teleporters. You can jump to the platform where the upper teleporter is (first north, then east), or just fall down to the ground and use the teleporters to get up there.\nFrom the upper teleporter, climb up the ladder to the north. Turn to your left and jump to the platform in the southeast corner. Climb up the ladder, then partially down the other side (west). Jump off, performing a back-flip, onto the next platform.\nPluck &lt;a href=\"The%20Flower%20that%20doesn%27t%20Exist\"&gt;The Flower that doesn't Exist&lt;/a&gt; and loot the &lt;a href=\"chest\"&gt;chest&lt;/a&gt; on the ledge. \nBring the flower to &lt;a href=\"Chanelle\"&gt;Chanelle&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Chez%20Chanelle\"&gt;Chez Chanelle&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Lanilor%20Lane\"&gt;Lanilor Lane&lt;/a&gt;. She will ask you to come back later when she has had some time to brew the perfume. Return to her after a bit and she will give you the bottle of &lt;a href=\"Baldini%27s%20Bouquet%20%28item%29\"&gt;Baldini's Bouquet perfume&lt;/a&gt; to bring to Baldini. (You need to exit Chez Chanelle, enter &amp; exit a different building, then return for her to complete the perfume.) She lowers her prices upon giving it to you.\nReturn to Baldini and give him the perfume to complete the quest."}
