{"id": "22558", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=22558", "title": "Begin the Blessing Ritual", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quests\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDetailed Walkthrough.\n is a main quest gained after all members of the council are gathered and the player has spoken with Zandalor who asks the player to sound the gong. The ritual begins immediately after the gong is sounded, which will result in a cutscene to play.\nBefore sounding the gong make sure all quests are completed, otherwise they will be marked as failed. Items which are not in your inventory will be lost."}
