{"id": "19174", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19174", "title": "Blank Air Skillbook", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20miscellaneous%20items\"&gt;crafting component&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nBlank air skillbook is a book which when combined with an appropriate scroll containing a &lt;a href=\"Aerotheurge%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;aerotheurge&lt;/a&gt; spell, may create a skillbook of said spell. Its weight is 0.3 and value is 250 gold.\nBase blank air skillbook can be used to craft aerotheurge skills from Starter to Adept tier (up to level 9 skills). High tier blank air skillbook can be used to craft aerotheurge skillbooks of all tiers.\nCrafting.\nIn order to be able to craft this item the Gift Bag: Herb Gardens must be activated as it enables to grow and purchase &lt;a href=\"Distinctive%20Tea\"&gt;Distinctive Tea&lt;/a&gt; which is a key ingredient. Note that activating any Gift Bag disables achievments."}
{"id": "19168", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19168", "title": "Blank Earth Skillbook", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20miscellaneous%20items\"&gt;crafting component&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nBlank earth skillbook is a book which when combined with an appropriate scroll containing a &lt;a href=\"Geomancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;geomancer&lt;/a&gt; spell, may create a skillbook of said spell. Blank earth skill book weight is 0.3 and value is 250 gold. They can be used to craft geomancer skills from Starter to Adept tier (up to level 9 skills).\nHigh tier blank earth skillbook is book which may be combined with any scroll containing a geomancer spell, to create a skillbook of all geomancer tiers. Its weight is 0.3 and value is 400 gold.\nCrafting.\nIn order to be able to craft this item the Gift Bag: Herb Gardens must be activated as it enables to grow and purchase &lt;a href=\"Distinctive%20Amadouvier\"&gt;Distinctive Amadouvier&lt;/a&gt; which is a key ingredient. Note that activating any Gift Bag disables achievments."}
{"id": "21642", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21642", "title": "Blank Fire Skillbook", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20miscellaneous%20items\"&gt;crafting component&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nBlank fire skillbook is a book which when combined with an appropriate scroll containing a &lt;a href=\"Pyrokinetic%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;pyrokinetic&lt;/a&gt; spell, may create a skillbook of said spell. Its weight is 0.3 and value is 250 gold.\nBase blank fire skillbook can be used to craft pyrokinetic skills from Starter to Adept tier (up to level 9 skills). High tier blank fire skillbook can be used to craft pyrokinetic skillbooks of all tiers.\nCrafting.\nIn order to be able to craft this item the Gift Bag: Herb Gardens must be activated as it enables to grow and purchase &lt;a href=\"Distinctive%20Boletus\"&gt;Distinctive Boletus&lt;/a&gt; which is a key ingredient. Note that activating any Gift Bag disables achievments.\nUsage.\nFollowing table shows all items for which this item is used for."}
{"id": "19172", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19172", "title": "Blank Necromancy Skillbook", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20miscellaneous%20items\"&gt;crafting component&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nBlank necromancy skillbook is a book which when combined with an appropriate scroll containing a &lt;a href=\"Necromancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;necromancy&lt;/a&gt; spell, may create a skillbook of said spell. Its weight is 0.3 and value is 250 gold. They can be used to craft necromancer skills from Starter to Adept tier (up to level 9 skills).\nHigh tier blank necromancy skillbook is book which may be combined with any scroll containing a necromancy spell, to create a skillbook or all necromancer tiers. Its weight is 0.3 and value is 400 gold.\nCrafting.\nIn order to be able to craft this item the Gift Bag: Herb Gardens must be activated as it enables to grow and purchase &lt;a href=\"Distinctive%20Trumpet%20of%20Death\"&gt;Distinctive Trumpet of Death&lt;/a&gt; which is a key ingredient. Note that activating any Gift Bag disables achievments."}
