{"id": "12281", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12281", "title": "Blessed Smoke Cloud", "text": "Blessed Smoke Cloud is an &lt;a href=\"Aerotheurge%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Aerotheurge&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; source skill in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nBlessed smoke cloud conjures a cloud of thick blessed smoke that makes characters Invisible. The cloud will also remove \"Silenced\" status. After 2 turns the blessed cloud will transform into smoke cloud that will remain for 1 turn.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into both &lt;a href=\"Aerotheurge%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Aerotheurge&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 500 gold. A skillbook can be crafted by combining any &lt;a href=\"Aerotheurge%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Aerotheurge&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks out of which atleast one must be a source skillbook. Since is a mixed source skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nThis skill cannot be bought or stolen from NPCs in the game."}
{"id": "17017", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17017", "title": "Blessed Water Arrow", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a special arrow which deals no damage and instead restores Vitality of all characters in area of impact (2 turns). Unless affected characters are &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; which will cause them to take physical damage instead. Additionally this arrow will create a blessed water surface (2 meters). \nCharacters need to wield &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Weapons\"&gt;bow or crossbow&lt;/a&gt; in order to use this arrow. The healing factor of the arrow depends on: base damage of the wielded weapon, &lt;a href=\"Finesse\"&gt;Finesse&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and height (bonus from height difference is affected by &lt;a href=\"Huntsman\"&gt;Huntsman&lt;/a&gt;).\nSince is a special arrow it is affected by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Arrow Recovery&lt;/a&gt; talent which grants 33 % chance to recover a special arrow after firing it. It is possible to increase the range of the arrow by 2 meters through the &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Far Out Man&lt;/a&gt; talent."}
