{"id": "15214", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15214", "title": "Blind (Divine Divinity)", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20skills%23Way%20of%20the%20survivor\"&gt;survivor skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nAvailable once &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; reaches level 8, blind reduces the target's &lt;a href=\"sight\"&gt;sight&lt;/a&gt; for a fixed period of time, starting at rank one with an initial reduction of 20% for 5 seconds and going up to a 100% reduction for 15 seconds at rank five. The reduction increases by 20% per rank and the effective time increases by 5 seconds every other rank."}
